*vm-8.0.3.495 (19 Aug 2007)

  19 Aug 2007; Ulrich Mueller <ulm@gentoo.org> -vm-8.0.1.465.ebuild,
  +vm-8.0.3.495.ebuild:
  Version bump.

*vm-8.0.2.487 (25 Jul 2007)

  25 Jul 2007; Ulrich Mueller <ulm@gentoo.org> +vm-8.0.2.487.ebuild:
  Version bump. DESTDIR is supported now.

  14 Jul 2007; Ulrich Mueller <ulm@gentoo.org> vm-8.0.1.465.ebuild:
  Use "emake -j1 install" to guarantee that the installed .elc files have a
  newer time stamp than the .el files.

*vm-8.0.1.465 (13 Jul 2007)

  13 Jul 2007; Ulrich Mueller <ulm@gentoo.org> files/50vm-gentoo.el,
  +files/vm-8.0-no-pcrisis.patch, +vm-8.0.1.465.ebuild:
  Major version bump. Updated HOMEPAGE, SRC_URI, and LICENSE; ebuild
  completely redone.

  13 Jul 2007; Diego Pettenò <flameeyes@gentoo.org> vm-7.19.282.ebuild:
  Replace mkdirhier with mkdir -p to avoid depending on x11-misc/imake. Thanks
  to Andrea Veroni for finding out.

  20 May 2007; Raúl Porcel <armin76@gentoo.org>
