*vm-7.19.282 (16 Apr 2007)

  16 Apr 2007; Ulrich Mueller <ulm@gentoo.org> +vm-7.19.282.ebuild:
  Version bump (copied from Emacs overlay). Include patches and addons from
  the new upstream maintainer Robert Widhopf-Fenk. Added some die comments;
  use emake instead of make; introduced bbdb USE flag and dependency.

*vm-7.19-r3 (06 Apr 2007)

  06 Apr 2007; Christian Faulhammer <opfer@gentoo.org>
